    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a new SRv6 network function which can be used for SRv6 Network Resource Programming. A new SRv6 Endpoint behavior is used to associate with a set of network resource partition, called End.NRP. By using the End.NRP SID , the SRv6 policy can provide the capability of network resources programming.</t>
